OL,3,CFive Iranian women footballers seek
OL,4,Crefuge in Australia
OL,6,FFive players from the Iranian women's
OL,7,Fnational football team have left the
OL,8,Fteam's training camp and successfully
OL,9,Fsought refuge in Australia, according
OL,10,Fto the former shah's son.
OL,12,FThe five players were moved to the
OL,13,Fsafe house, managed by the Australian
OL,14,FFederal Police and other authorities,
OL,15,Ffrom their Gold Coast hotel earlier on
OL,16,FMonday, ITV News' US Partner CNN.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
