PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773133490
OL,3,CFive Iranian women footballers seek
OL,4,Crefuge in Australia
OL,6,FConcerns were raised for the safety of
OL,7,Fmembers of the team following their
OL,8,Fdefeat in the AFC Women's Asian Cup
OL,9,Fafter they were labelled traitors by
OL,10,Fmembers of the Iranian regime for
OL,11,Fstaying silent during the national
OL,12,Fanthem at the beginning of their first
OL,13,Fmatch last week.
OL,15,FSources told ITV News that the team
OL,16,Fwas forced to sing the national anthem
OL,17,Fahead of their second match on
OL,18,FThursday, and again on Sunday before
OL,19,Ftheir 0-2 defeat to the Philippines,
OL,20,Fwhere they also saluted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773133490
OL,3,CFive Iranian women footballers seek
OL,4,Crefuge in Australia
OL,6,FReza Pahlavi, the son of Iran's ousted
OL,7,Fshah, had joined calls for the women's
OL,8,Fsafety to be ensured by the Australian
OL,9,Fgovernment. He named the footballers
OL,10,Fwho he said had fled the team for
OL,11,Fsafety as Fatemeh Pasandideh, Zahra
OL,12,FGhanbari, Zahra Sarbali, Atefeh
OL,13,FRamazanzadeh and Mona Hamoudi.
OL,15,FWriting on X, he added: "These five
OL,16,Fcourageous athletes, currently in a
OL,17,Fsafe location, have announced that
OL,18,Fthey have joined Iran's national Lion
OL,19,Fand Sun Revolution."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773133490
OL,3,CFive Iranian women footballers seek
OL,4,Crefuge in Australia
OL,6,FThe Lion and Sun refer to the original
OL,7,Femblem on Iran's national flag that
OL,8,Fwas replaced by an emblem representing
OL,9,Fthe word "Allah" and the phrase "God
OL,10,Fis Great" (Allahu akbar) after the
OL,11,F1979 revolution.
OL,13,FEarlier, Pahlavi had said the women
OL,14,Fwould face "dire consequences" if they
OL,15,Freturned to Iran.
OL,17,FHe said: "I call on the Australian
OL,18,Fgovernment to ensure their safety and
OL,19,Fgive them any and all needed support."
