OL,3,CFive Iranian women footballers seek
OL,4,Crefuge in Australia
OL,6,FThe war between the US, Israel and
OL,7,FIran has entered its second week, with
OL,8,Fseeminly little appetite for de-
OL,9,Fescalation.
OL,11,FThe Iranian Red Crescent reports that
OL,12,Fmore than 1,200 people in Iran have
OL,13,Fbeen killed since the war broke out on
OL,14,FFebruary 28. The attacks come just
OL,15,Fover a month after Iran's theocratic
OL,16,Fregime killed tens of thousands in a
OL,17,Fruthless crackdown on protests that
OL,18,Fbegan in demonstrations against the
OL,19,Fincreasingly dire economic crisis and
OL,20,Fswelled to encompass dissatisfaction
OL,21,Fwith the government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
