OL,3,CFive Iranian women footballers seek
OL,4,Crefuge in Australia
OL,6,FSeveral footballers were among those
OL,7,Fkilled in the protests.
OL,9,FAfter the loss in their final match of
OL,10,Fthe tournament on Sunday, supporters
OL,11,Fcrowded around the Iranian team bus,
OL,12,Fshouting at police to "save our girls"
OL,13,Fas it pulled away. Hadi Karimi, a
OL,14,Fhuman rights advocate and member of
OL,15,Fthe local Iranian community, said
OL,16,Fsupporters outside the bus could
OL,17,Fclearly see at least three players
OL,18,Finside making the international hand
OL,19,Fsignal for help.
OL,26,@tD@WOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
