OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773133490
OL,3,CFive Iranian women footballers seek
OL,4,Crefuge in Australia
OL,6,FHowever, a source close to the team
OL,7,Fexpressed scepticism to CNN that the
OL,8,Fteam members would know what the sign
OL,9,Frepresents.
OL,11,FCraig Foster, a former Australian
OL,12,Finternational and human rights
OL,13,Fadvocate, said "a vast range of
OL,14,Forganisations" had tried to speak with
OL,15,Fthe women during their time in
OL,16,FAustralia but had been denied the
OL,17,Fopportunity.
OL,26,@uD@POUvD@NO]
