OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773133490
OL,3,CFive Iranian women footballers seek
OL,4,Crefuge in Australia
OL,6,F"The first thing that the Australian
OL,7,Ffootball community is calling on them
OL,8,Fis to grant access to the players to
OL,9,Fsafe, culturally appropriate support
OL,10,Fnetworks, so that they can privately
OL,11,Fand confidentially express if they are
OL,12,Ffeeling unsafe and what they would
OL,13,Flike to see happen," he said.
