OL,3,CFive Iranian women footballers seek
OL,4,Crefuge in Australia
OL,6,FAt a post-match press conference on
OL,7,FSunday, Iran coach Marziyeh Jafari
OL,8,Fsaid the women's team were keen to
OL,9,Freturn home.
OL,11,F"Personally, I would like to return to
OL,12,Fmy country as soon as possible and be
OL,13,Fwith my compatriots and family," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
